{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975270/extras/gif_8.gif?t=1732359247\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Introduction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to Inventory Quest: Hero's Hoard, where you take on the crucial role of managing and optimizing your hero's inventory and loadout instead of directly controlling them in action-packed battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this unique twist on the RPG genre, strategic decision-making takes center stage as you carefully choose and equip items to keep your hero effective and alive. From powerful weapons to life-saving potions, every item plays a vital role in your hero's success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One run takes only few minutes and tests the player's ability to optimize loadout and manage their inventory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do whatever it takes to survive. Stunlock enemies or maximize hp regen to become almost an immortal. Would you discard an armor for precious space in the inventory or keep it for possible set bonus? You decide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a challenging journey where your tactical decisions determine your hero's fate. Will you rise to the challenge and master the art of loadout optimization?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Keep potions in the belt</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975270/extras/gif_5.gif?t=1732359247\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Collect armor sets</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975270/extras/gif_7.gif?t=1732359247\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Don't run out of weapons!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975270/extras/gif_6.gif?t=1732359247\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Prepare for the bossfights!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975270/extras/gif_4.gif?t=1732359247\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Meet the mysterious merchant</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975270/extras/gif_2.gif?t=1732359247\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Strategic Inventory Management:</strong> Equip items from your hero's inventory to optimize their loadout for battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Weight Management:</strong> Keep an eye on the weight indicator to ensure your hero can carry all their gear without being burdened.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Potions and Belts:</strong> Combine potions and equip them on your hero's belt for quick access during combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Durability management:</strong> Equip optimal weapons to minimize their wear while the combat is resolved automatically.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Stat Allocation and Leveling:</strong> Allocate stat points as your hero levels up to suit your loadout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rare Item Abilities: </strong>Discover rare items with special abilities that can turn the tide of battle in your favor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Merchant: </strong>Trade your items with the mysterious merchant.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Knight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2975270/64ce9dfaa7077ffef4e8f33da03dbfcc7398d05e.jpg"},{"name":"Orc","path":"https://cdn.aka